OpenLH README file
=================

INTRO
~~~~~
OpenLH code is placed in the src directory.


DEPENDENCIES
~~~~~~~~~~~~
 * Python2.5+
 * pygtk2.10 (gtk.StatusIcon)
 * python-gnutls

OPTIONAL DEPENDENCIES
 * pynotify
 * python-mysql
 * python-postgres
 * python-gnome-desktop

